Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister, Umaru, is renowned for her beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're staying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, today's Saturday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be back tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's your day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why you're a corporate slave\Nto a wicked company that steals your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our deadline's right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'll get some time off in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation's over, so even though\NI won't be around, you better not stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free, FREE I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My night is just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother always goes\Nto sleep before midnight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to bed already, or I won't\Nbe able to wake up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the time to burn through all my games!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just never seem to have enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bulldozer. It will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! That's super rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm going to wake up Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He always gets mad, so I just acted out of reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what time it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Big Brother said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you some breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stir-fried bell peppers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now THIS is good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop eating cup noodles so late at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink all the soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Late-night potato chips and cola sure hit the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late, so keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit eating those potato chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop chugging it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, no one can get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have everything in the palm of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Umaru shall be held down by NO ONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world where nights are long and glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I thought it was 1:00 AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, time flies at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to check what late-night anime are on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning. Get up, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hng... what? It's morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed up late, so I slept in more than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've burned through 16 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought if I went out, I could\Nget back some of what I'd burned through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Burned through"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to be out at night.\NHurry up and get back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what's going on, but... I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "attendance optional," right? No one's gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's still September! It'll be hot! You go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the landlord might find that a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "Umaru is such a nice girl,\Nso I thought for sure she'd come."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My, I'm glad to see some youngsters showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, my back is giving me some problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Big Brother... let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? There aren't even that many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya! Hya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! T-Taihei and Umaru! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I only just got started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Ebina. You've already pulled all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Well, back home in Akita,\Nreckon I... I mean, I'm used to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a world apart from Umaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm glad you're both here.\NHonestly, I was a little lonely on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah. I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's hard for her to go running off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we do this together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... so, should I cut these with a sickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I think it'd be best to pull them by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to pull them by the roots\Nor else they'll grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? This is... kind of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant weed spotted dead ahead!\NThat must be the middle boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! I quit! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can if you want.\NBig Brother! I quit! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dragging out here in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya! Hya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished up pretty fast, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It feels like we've really done something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, your face is all red.\NAre you having a heatstroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I super really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we all treat ourselves\Nby getting something cold to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Great idea, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A soccer match?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My school shall be holding it this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I must practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that move just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop kicking your food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just something I do at home sometimes,\Nthe Potato Catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite good at ball games, yes? Please, teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn and I are always battling each other,\Nbut the soccer match will be class vs. class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This might make it easier to talk to her at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can keep up with my training regimen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Osu! Is commonly used in martial arts circles as a way of not only\Nagreeing, but to also show determination.\NOSU! Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't watch the ball. Instead,\Nsee the trajectory of where the ball is GOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentality is a big part of sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to visualize you've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you take your shot,\Nthe ball should spin like a bullet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,like you're blasting it with a laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball is your best friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball is your lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your stamina for when you'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take some breaks during the game. Rest is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I rest, I will have points detracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Soccer is a team sport.\NJust take your break and trust in the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be at the same school,\Nin the same class as you, UMR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the people in your class are good at soccer too.\NNow take what I've taught you and go WIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these are the uniforms we'll all be wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect Umaru... I will protect Umaru...\NI WILL protect Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was on the same team as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our uniforms are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get this match underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take your places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, who are these people?\NMost of them aren't even in our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They split up our classes\Nwhen they were making the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The students were getting too fired up about it\Nbeing class vs. class, so they scrapped the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to balance out the teams, and made the\Nperson with the best grades in PE the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The person with the best grades is the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Your leader hasn't gotten here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shapaaaaaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's standing on some balls\Nand sliding around on them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's water skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbwaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trained quite extensively!\NIt is through soccer that I shall defeat Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it looks like it's almost time for kickoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This match will be between Arayada High's Team T...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and their opponent, Team U!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Sylphyn has shot forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See the trajectory of where the ball is GOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbwaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now THAT'S fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her form is all over the place,\Nbut her power is remarkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is now:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Canzone Sylphyn Bullet Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast! Is this a done deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NKirie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a misdirection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie has changed the ball's trajectory\Nand sent it straight to Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to fight alongside Sylphyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but still... I'm going to give this all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see its trajectory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru and Sylphyn are locked in a heated battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what the caption at the bottom there\Nmeans, but is that a universe I see forming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've had to deal with\Nso many surprises that now I feel weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,GOAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The first point of the game goes to Team T!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn pulled it off all on her own, and despite\Nhow far she ran, she's not breathing heavy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I pushed myself a bit too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That play just now took a lot out of me.\NRegardless, I must score another point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sylphyn! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Team U has rallied around Umaru\Nand is holding their own against Team T!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Sylphyn has turned\NTeam T into a one-man show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie! Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umaru is cheering me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take... Take THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This shot has given the ball a strange gyration!\NBut will it hit net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, the judge who witnessed this mysterious\Nincident explained it as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, a ball strikes\Nand then rebounds like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball hit a sort of soft obstruction,\Nresulting in a motion nothing short of miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could have predicted\Nwhat the ball would do next! Put simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It scored a picture-perfect goal against Team T.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an OWN GOAL! That's as good as any!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "good" at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't allow you to score!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What turn of events is this?\NTeam U is starting to pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the other team keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're in the zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Team U has reached that ultimate\Nstate of focus known as "the zone"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(For more about this "zone," please see\Nwhichever sports manga is applicable.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But how? How can there be such\Na difference between our teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, defeat is certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced so hard, and even\Nreceived instruction from... UMR!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Soccer is a team sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanabe! Take a wide right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Daimoji! Cover Sakura a bit so she can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,U-understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, they're moving a lot more coordinated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TSF!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Team U came from behind for the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were great, Sylphyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you fire off that "Bullet Shot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You scored two points against\NUmaru's team, and that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, your coaching in the second half was fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You even remembered all our names, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please teach us soccer sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the soccer match came to a close...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be having a volleyball tournament soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope we can train together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the next ball match was already\Nright around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's all walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're that girl from the class next door, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Haruka! C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I don't even know you,\Nso stop talking like you're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't sweat the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez... well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear... Haruka is always making friends\Nwith that dazzling smile of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Making friends with a simple greeting\Nlike that sure would make things easier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, it is what it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even asking someone to hang out\Nis way too much pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you ask and they say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be heartbroken, and you won't even have a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, let's walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being WAY too dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If that sort of thing holds you back,\Nyou'll just regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have lots of friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, you and Umaru made some\Nawesome combo plays at the soccer match!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, I wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphyn, do you understand this question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like people are talking to Kirie and Sylphyn\Na lot more after the soccer match...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try talking to people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm embarrassed for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... what would I do if they're not interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I've always been the one\Nthat other people talk to first...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kirie has club activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't in her class, so I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I joined a club,\NI could get good at sports like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about the soccer match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I made so many mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Sylphyn was kind enough to pass the ball to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about talking to Sylphyn after that,\Nbut she said she had to talk to a friend and just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, you've asked Kirie\Nto have lunch with you before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you afraid she'd say "No"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was embarrassed and a little unsure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I felt I'd regret it if I didn't try!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm going to look for Sylphyn, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! Our tests are coming up, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Um, they're cleaning the pool today,\Nso club activities are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how about the four of us walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you certainly are asking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, fine, I have no objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes, YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So those four are friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we go! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm yourself, Sylphyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say we get some crepes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, this is serious! Our anime has started up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, just relax, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to be so calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I CAN HAVE MY OWN THOUGHTS ABOUT STUFF\NAND THE STUFF I THINK ABOUT IS MINE AND STUFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs to relax.
